{"tid":2450593,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個自己嘅原子筆演變史","createTime":"2021-03-17T13:42:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T09:12:57.000Z","uid":182219,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"1a7dbb097680926f47c52cd0abd5b838a3d03812","tid":2450593,"uid":182219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T13:42:51.000Z","msg":"我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最近發覺自己會有一段時間用定某隻原子筆嘅偏好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小學初初開始接觸原子筆係用呢隻Pilot BP筆<br />\n我稱佢為老野筆<br />\n純粹係因為嗰陣時嘅中文老師話好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得寫字嗰時會有啲撻撻聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一直用到升中學<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XdjavmM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXdjavmM.png&h=45e75024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到咗中學階段 中一二時<br />\n因為學生會有文具部<br />\n就買左Pilot rexgrip轉吓新鮮感 <br />\n發覺又幾好寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就係咁比我寵幸左成個初中階段<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KgGXam1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKgGXam1.jpg&h=74579c82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去到高form <br />\nPilot rexgrip遇到第三者<br />\n就係Uni 既 Laklock<br />\n用咗佢覺得啲字寫得纖幼又靚 <br />\n一定要用0.4 <br />\n嗰時真係愛不釋手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8hpRePG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8hpRePG.png&h=86004fd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去到大學階段<br />\n返學有日冇筆用 <br />\n見到個位附近有枝筆就借左黎用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然係有借冇還啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢就係我用到而家出黎做野都用緊嘅<br />\nZebra Sarasa Clip<br />\n佢真係好滑 <br />\n用0.5芯真係點寫都覺得自己寫得好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢啲芯有唔同粗幼 但唔係度度齊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WWRweP3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWWRweP3.jpg&h=2a06bd93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講完到你"},{"pid":"25746e6c2be56a5a806db8f9be185923598f76ca","tid":2450593,"uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T13:56:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXdjavmM.png&amp;h=45e75024&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n藍色無敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1043cd8cd5855886025d738c5dffc0f2f290d8f","tid":2450593,"uid":36164,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T13:57:31.000Z","msg":"G2，用用吓甩珠就換枝新嘅<br />\n完"},{"pid":"e394b25cae0beaf4d0c2e17d97bc9783f359d470","tid":2450593,"uid":62731,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:02:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://csstationery.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Pilot_ballpen.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcsstationery.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2FPilot_ballpen.jpg&h=2479a650&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用開呢隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2123fe3f47d9a986ff38e4730280963bb923fcf1","tid":2450593,"uid":90820,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:03:32.000Z","msg":"以前中學用開呢隻<br />\n兩三蚊枝<br />\n跌極都唔斷墨<br />\n好抵屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b9BXavD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb9BXavD.jpg&h=b68f1493&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bPyeXaL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi